fGM.Description: Normalized fractional volume of grey matter: fGM  = GMsum / (GMsum + WMsum + CSFsum)

fWM.Description: Normalized fractional volume of white matter: fWM  = WMsum / (GMsum + WMsum + CSFsum)

fCSF.Description: Normalized fractional volume of Cerebrospinal Fluid: fCSF  = CSFsum / (GMsum + WMsum + CSFsum)
